ged to help with transport? There is nothing in anyone's contract about working in different locations. The away days are mandatory and refusing won't go down well with senior management.</strong></p><p></p><p>Do you need advice on a work issue? For Jeremy's and readers' help, send a brief email to <a href=\"mailto:dear.jeremy@theguardian.com\" title=\"\">dear.jeremy@theguardian.com</a>. Please note that he is unable to answer questions of a legal nature or reply personally.</p>","headline":"Should a company pay expenses for away days?","trailText":"<strong>Work advice </strong>I am required to drive much further than normal to attend a mandatory office away day, and will be out of pocket","shouldHideAdverts":"false","publication":"theguardian.com","showInRelatedContent":"true","shortUrl":"http://gu.com/p/3m5n5","thumbnail":"http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Money/Pix/pictures/2014/1/23/1390493257791/Car-speedometer-showing-p-006.jpg","secureThumbnail":"https://static-secure.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Money/Pix/pictures/2014/1/23/1390493257791/Car-speedometer-showing-p-006.jpg","wordcount":"216","commentable":"true","internalContentCode":"427861583","allowUgc":"false","internalOctopusCode":"8595584","isPremoderated":"false","newspaperEditionDate":"2014-01-23T00:00:00Z","internalPageCode":"2031620","productionOffice":"UK","liveBloggingNow":"false","commentCloseDate":"2014-01-31T07:00:09Z"},"rights":{"syndicatable":false,"subscriptionDatabases":false},"webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/money/work-blog/2014/jan/24/company-pay-expenses-away-days","apiUrl":"http://internal.content.guardianapis.com/money/work-blog/2014/jan/24/company-pay-expenses-away-days","tags":[{"id":"money/series/dearjeremy","webTitle":"Dear Jeremy","type":"series","sectionId":"money","sectionName":"Money","webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/money/series/dearjeremy","apiUrl":"http://internal.content.guardianapis.com/money/series/dearjeremy","references":[]},{"id":"money/work-and-careers","webTitle":"